{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Rom|1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":1,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":1,"text":"Paul, a servant of Christ Jesus, called as an apostle and set apart for the gospel of God —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":2,"text":"which he promised beforehand through his prophets in the Holy Scriptures —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":3,"text":"concerning his Son, Jesus Christ our Lord, who was a descendant of David according to the flesh","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":4,"text":"and was appointed to be the powerful Son of God according to the Spirit of holiness by the resurrection of the dead.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":5,"text":"Through him we have received grace and apostleship to bring about the obedience of faith for the sake of his name among all the Gentiles,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":6,"text":"including you who are also called by Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":7,"text":"To all who are in Rome, loved by God, called as saints. Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":8,"text":"First, I thank my God through Jesus Christ for all of you because the news of your faith is being reported in all the world.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":9,"text":"God is my witness, whom I serve with my spirit in telling the good news about his Son —that I constantly mention you,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":10,"text":"always asking in my prayers that if it is somehow in God’s will, I may now at last succeed in coming to you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":11,"text":"For I want very much to see you, so that I may impart to you some spiritual gift to strengthen you,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":12,"text":"that is, to be mutually encouraged by each other’s faith, both yours and mine.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":13,"text":"Now I don’t want you to be unaware, brothers and sisters, that I often planned to come to you (but was prevented until now ) in order that I might have a fruitful ministry among you, just as I have had among the rest of the Gentiles.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":14,"text":"I am obligated both to Greeks and barbarians, both to the wise and the foolish.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":15,"text":"So I am eager to preach the gospel to you also who are in Rome.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":16,"text":"For I am not ashamed of the gospel, because it is the power of God for salvation to everyone who believes, first to the Jew, and also to the Greek.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":17,"text":"For in it the righteousness of God is revealed from faith to faith, just as it is written: The righteous will live by faith.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":18,"text":"For God’s wrath is revealed from heaven against all godlessness and unrighteousness of people who by their unrighteousness suppress the truth,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":19,"text":"since what can be known about God is evident among them, because God has shown it to them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":20,"text":"For his invisible attributes, that is, his eternal power and divine nature, have been clearly seen since the creation of the world, being understood through what he has made. As a result, people are without excuse.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":21,"text":"For though they knew God, they did not glorify him as God or show gratitude. Instead, their thinking became worthless, and their senseless hearts were darkened.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:22","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":22,"text":"Claiming to be wise, they became fools","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:23","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":23,"text":"and exchanged the glory of the immortal God for images resembling mortal man, birds, four-footed animals, and reptiles.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:24","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":24,"text":"Therefore God delivered them over in the desires of their hearts to sexual impurity, so that their bodies were degraded among themselves.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:25","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":25,"text":"They exchanged the truth of God for a lie, and worshiped and served what has been created instead of the Creator, who is praised forever. Amen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:26","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":26,"text":"For this reason God delivered them over to disgraceful passions. Their women exchanged natural sexual relations for unnatural ones.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:27","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":27,"text":"The men in the same way also left natural relations with women and were inflamed in their lust for one another. Men committed shameless acts with men and received in their own persons the appropriate penalty of their error.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:28","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":28,"text":"And because they did not think it worthwhile to acknowledge God, God delivered them over to a corrupt mind so that they do what is not right.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:29","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":29,"text":"They are filled with all unrighteousness, evil, greed, and wickedness. They are full of envy, murder, quarrels, deceit, and malice. They are gossips,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:30","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":30,"text":"slanderers, God-haters, arrogant, proud, boastful, inventors of evil, disobedient to parents,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:31","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":31,"text":"senseless, untrustworthy, unloving, and unmerciful.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:32","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","bookOrder":44,"chapter":1,"verse":32,"text":"Although they know God’s just sentence —that those who practice such things deserve to die —they not only do them, but even applaud others who practice them.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Rom","chapter":1,"paragraphStarts":[1,7,8,13,16,18,24,26,28],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"The Gospel of God for Rome"},{"beforeVerse":8,"text":"Paul’s Desire to Visit Rome"},{"beforeVerse":16,"text":"The Righteous Will Live by Faith"},{"beforeVerse":18,"text":"The Guilt of the Gentile World"},{"beforeVerse":26,"text":"From Idolatry to Depravity"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Paul, a servant of Christ Jesus, called as an apostle "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or Jesus, a called apostle"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:1","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:1","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 1:1","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and set apart "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:2","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":2,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:15","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" for the gospel of God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 1:14","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 1:1","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 9:1","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"2Co 1:1","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15},{"label":"Ac 13:2","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":2},{"label":"Gl 1:15","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":15},{"label":"Mk 1:14","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or Jesus, a called apostle"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"which he promised beforehand "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ti 1:2","book":"Tit","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" through his prophets "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 1:70","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":70,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:21","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:26","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" in the Holy Scriptures — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ti 1:2","book":"Tit","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"Lk 1:70","book":"Luk","chapter":1,"verse":70},{"label":"Rm 3:21","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":21},{"label":"Rm 16:26","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"concerning his Son, Jesus Christ our Lord, who was a descendant of David "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit was of the seed of David"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 1:1","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to the flesh "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 4:1","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:3","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":3,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:5","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:18","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":18,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 1:1","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Jn 1:14","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":14},{"label":"Rm 4:1","book":"Rom","chapter":4,"verse":1},{"label":"Rm 9:3","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":3},{"label":"Rm 9:5","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":5},{"label":"1Co 10:18","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Lit was of the seed of David"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and was appointed to be the powerful "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 10:38","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":38,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:33","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:31","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":31,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 26:23","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":23,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" Son of God "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 4:3","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" according to the Spirit of holiness "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or the spirit of holiness, or the Holy Spirit"},{"kind":"text","text":" by the resurrection of the dead. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 10:38","book":"Act","chapter":10,"verse":38},{"label":"Ac 13:33","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":33},{"label":"Ac 17:31","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":31},{"label":"Ac 26:23","book":"Act","chapter":26,"verse":23},{"label":"Mt 4:3","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Or the spirit of holiness, or the Holy Spirit"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Through him we have received grace and apostleship "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 1:25","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to bring about "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Or him for; lit him into"},{"kind":"text","text":" the obedience "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 6:7","book":"Act","chapter":6,"verse":7,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:26","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":26,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of faith for the sake of his name among all the Gentiles, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":5,"text":"Or nations, also in v. 13"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 1:25","book":"Act","chapter":1,"verse":25},{"label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Ac 6:7","book":"Act","chapter":6,"verse":7},{"label":"Rm 16:26","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":26},{"label":"Ac 9:15","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[{"marker":4,"text":"Or him for; lit him into"},{"marker":5,"text":"Or nations, also in v. 13"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:6","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"including you who are also called by Jesus Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jd 1:1","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 17:14","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":14,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jd 1:1","book":"Jud","chapter":1,"verse":1},{"label":"Rv 17:14","book":"Rev","chapter":17,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:7","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"To all who are in Rome, loved by God, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:5","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:39","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":39,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:4","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" called "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:24","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" as saints. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:2–4","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 5:5","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":5},{"label":"Rm 8:39","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":39},{"label":"1Th 1:4","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":4},{"label":"Rm 8:28","book":"Rom","chapter":8,"verse":28},{"label":"1Co 1:24","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":24},{"label":"1Co 1:2–4","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:8","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"First, I thank my God through Jesus Christ for all of you because the news of your faith "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or because your faith"},{"kind":"text","text":" is being reported in all the world. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 16:19","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 16:19","book":"Rom","chapter":16,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or because your faith"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:9","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"God is my witness, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:1","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 1:23","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:31","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":31,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:8","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:5","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 2:10","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":10,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" whom I serve with my spirit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:3","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" in telling the good news about his Son —that I constantly mention you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 1:16","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:3–5","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 1:2","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":2,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:3","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":3,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Phm 4","book":"Phm","chapter":1,"verse":4,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 9:1","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"2Co 1:23","book":"2Co","chapter":1,"verse":23},{"label":"2Co 11:31","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":31},{"label":"Php 1:8","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"1Th 2:5","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"1Th 2:10","book":"1Th","chapter":2,"verse":10},{"label":"2Tm 1:3","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Eph 1:16","book":"Eph","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Php 1:3–5","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"1Th 1:2","book":"1Th","chapter":1,"verse":2},{"label":"2Tm 1:3","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":3},{"label":"Phm 4","book":"Phm","chapter":1,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"always asking in my prayers that if it is somehow in God’s will, I may now at last succeed in coming to you. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 18:21","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:32","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":32,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 18:21","book":"Act","chapter":18,"verse":21},{"label":"Rm 15:32","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":32}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I want very much to see you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:21","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:23","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":23,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that I may impart to you some spiritual gift to strengthen you, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 19:21","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":21},{"label":"Rm 15:23","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":23}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"that is, to be mutually encouraged by each other’s faith, both yours and mine."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Now I don’t want you to be unaware, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 10:1","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 11:3","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":3,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" brothers and sisters, that I often planned to come to you (but was prevented until now "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 19:21","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":") in order that I might have a fruitful ministry "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit have some fruit"},{"kind":"text","text":" among you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 4:36","book":"Jhn","chapter":4,"verse":36,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:16","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":16,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 1:22","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":22,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 1:6","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":6,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" just as I have had among the rest of the Gentiles. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 10:1","book":"1Co","chapter":10,"verse":1},{"label":"1Co 11:3","book":"1Co","chapter":11,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 19:21","book":"Act","chapter":19,"verse":21},{"label":"Jn 4:36","book":"Jhn","chapter":4,"verse":36},{"label":"Rm 15:16","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":16},{"label":"Php 1:22","book":"Php","chapter":1,"verse":22},{"label":"Col 1:6","book":"Col","chapter":1,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit have some fruit"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I am obligated both to Greeks and barbarians, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or non-Greeks"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 28:2","book":"Act","chapter":28,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" both to the wise and the foolish. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 28:2","book":"Act","chapter":28,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or non-Greeks"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So I am eager to preach the gospel "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 15:20","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 9:16","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":16,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to you also who are in Rome."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 15:20","book":"Rom","chapter":15,"verse":20},{"label":"1Co 9:16","book":"1Co","chapter":9,"verse":16}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For I am not ashamed of the gospel, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of Christ"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" because it is the power of God for salvation "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:18","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:24","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":24,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" to everyone who believes, first to the Jew, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:26","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":26,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 2:9","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":9,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"text","text":" and also to the Greek. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 7:35","book":"Jhn","chapter":7,"verse":35,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8},{"label":"2Tm 1:12","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":12},{"label":"2Tm 1:16","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"1Co 1:18","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":18},{"label":"1Co 1:24","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":24},{"label":"Ac 3:26","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":26},{"label":"Rm 2:9","book":"Rom","chapter":2,"verse":9},{"label":"Jn 7:35","book":"Jhn","chapter":7,"verse":35}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add of Christ"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For in it the righteousness of God is revealed from faith to faith, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or revealed out of faith into faith"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 3:21","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:30","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 3:9","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" just as it is written: The righteous will live by faith."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Or The one who is righteous by faith will live"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 3:11","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":11,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 10:38","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":38,"letter":"g"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 3:21","book":"Rom","chapter":3,"verse":21},{"label":"Rm 9:30","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":30},{"label":"Php 3:9","book":"Php","chapter":3,"verse":9},{"label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Hab 2:4","book":"Hab","chapter":2,"verse":4},{"label":"Gl 3:11","book":"Gal","chapter":3,"verse":11},{"label":"Heb 10:38","book":"Heb","chapter":10,"verse":38}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Or revealed out of faith into faith"},{"marker":3,"text":"Or The one who is righteous by faith will live"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For God’s wrath "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 5:9","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":9,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 5:6","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 3:6","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" is revealed from heaven against all godlessness and unrighteousness of people who by their unrighteousness suppress the truth, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Th 2:6–10","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":6,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 5:9","book":"Rom","chapter":5,"verse":9},{"label":"Eph 5:6","book":"Eph","chapter":5,"verse":6},{"label":"Col 3:6","book":"Col","chapter":3,"verse":6},{"label":"2Th 2:6–10","book":"2Th","chapter":2,"verse":6}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"since what can be known "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or what is known"},{"kind":"text","text":" about God is evident among them, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 14:17","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:24–27","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":24,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" because God has shown it to them. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ac 14:17","book":"Act","chapter":14,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 17:24–27","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":24}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or what is known"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For his invisible attributes, that is, his eternal power and divine nature, have been clearly seen since the creation of the world, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:6","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" being understood through what he has made. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 12:7","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 19:1–6","book":"Psa","chapter":19,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:21–22","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":21,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" As a result, people are without excuse. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 10:6","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":6},{"label":"Jb 12:7","book":"Job","chapter":12,"verse":7},{"label":"Ps 19:1–6","book":"Psa","chapter":19,"verse":1},{"label":"Jr 5:21–22","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For though they knew God, they did not glorify him as God or show gratitude. Instead, their thinking became worthless, and their senseless hearts were darkened. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Kg 17:15","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:5","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:17–20","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Kg 17:15","book":"2Ki","chapter":17,"verse":15},{"label":"Jr 2:5","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":5},{"label":"Eph 4:17–20","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":17}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Claiming to be wise, they became fools "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 10:14","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":14,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 1:20","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 10:14","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":14},{"label":"1Co 1:20","book":"1Co","chapter":1,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"and exchanged the glory of the immortal God for images resembling mortal man, birds, four-footed animals, and reptiles. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 106:20","book":"Psa","chapter":106,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 2:11","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 17:29","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":29,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 106:20","book":"Psa","chapter":106,"verse":20},{"label":"Jr 2:11","book":"Jer","chapter":2,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 17:29","book":"Act","chapter":17,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore God delivered them over in the desires of their hearts "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:3","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 4:19","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":19,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" to sexual impurity, so that their bodies were degraded among themselves. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Eph 2:3","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":3},{"label":"Eph 4:19","book":"Eph","chapter":4,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They exchanged the truth of God for a lie, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 44:20","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 10:14","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 13:25","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":25,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 16:19","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" and worshiped and served what has been created instead of the Creator, who is praised forever. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 9:5","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":5,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 11:31","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":31,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" Amen."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 44:20","book":"Isa","chapter":44,"verse":20},{"label":"Jr 10:14","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 13:25","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":25},{"label":"Jr 16:19","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":19},{"label":"Rm 9:5","book":"Rom","chapter":9,"verse":5},{"label":"2Co 11:31","book":"2Co","chapter":11,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For this reason God delivered them over to disgraceful passions. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Th 4:5","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Their women "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit females, also in v. 27"},{"kind":"text","text":" exchanged natural sexual relations "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Lit natural use, also in v. 27"},{"kind":"text","text":" for unnatural ones. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Th 4:5","book":"1Th","chapter":4,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit females, also in v. 27"},{"marker":2,"text":"Lit natural use, also in v. 27"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The men "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit males, also later in v."},{"kind":"text","text":" in the same way also left natural relations with women and were inflamed in their lust for one another. Men committed shameless acts with men "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:22","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 20:13","book":"Lev","chapter":20,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 6:9","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":9,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" and received in their own persons "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Or in themselves"},{"kind":"text","text":" the appropriate penalty of their error."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:22","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":22},{"label":"Lv 20:13","book":"Lev","chapter":20,"verse":13},{"label":"1Co 6:9","book":"1Co","chapter":6,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit males, also later in v."},{"marker":4,"text":"Or in themselves"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And because they did not think it worthwhile to acknowledge God, God delivered them over to a corrupt mind so that they do what is not right. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They are filled with all unrighteousness, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add sexual immorality"},{"kind":"text","text":" evil, greed, and wickedness. They are full of envy, murder, quarrels, deceit, and malice. They are gossips, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Co 12:20","book":"2Co","chapter":12,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Co 12:20","book":"2Co","chapter":12,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add sexual immorality"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"slanderers, God-haters, arrogant, proud, boastful, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 5:5","book":"Psa","chapter":5,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" inventors of evil, disobedient to parents, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 3:2","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 5:5","book":"Psa","chapter":5,"verse":5},{"label":"2Tm 3:2","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"senseless, untrustworthy, unloving, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss add unforgiving"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 3:3","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and unmerciful. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Tm 3:3","book":"2Ti","chapter":3,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss add unforgiving"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Rom:1:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Although they know God’s just sentence —that those who practice such things deserve to die "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":3,"text":"Lit things are worthy of death"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rm 6:21","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" —they not only do them, but even applaud "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":4,"text":"Lit even take pleasure in"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 11:48","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":48,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 22:20","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" others who practice them."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Rm 6:21","book":"Rom","chapter":6,"verse":21},{"label":"Lk 11:48","book":"Luk","chapter":11,"verse":48},{"label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 22:20","book":"Act","chapter":22,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[{"marker":3,"text":"Lit things are worthy of death"},{"marker":4,"text":"Lit even take pleasure in"}]}]},"cachedAt":1783279651896}